---
// Onboarding · Screen 4 — „Eve ist erst der Anfang." (der breite Blick)
//
// Läuft als vierte Sektion DERSELBEN /uebersicht-Seite (gleiches Backoffice-
// Layout/Chrome). Zentrierter Kopf + drei Säulen der Gästereise:
//   Vor der Anreise (Direktbuchung) · Während (Gästemappe + Eve — erledigt) ·
//   Nach (Wallet / WhatsApp / Wiederkehr).
// Ziel: Breite & Zukunftswert zeigen, ohne zu drängen. Leicht + überspringbar.
// Copy DE-only.
---

<section class="onb4" data-onb-step="4" style="display:none">
  <div class="onb4-body">

    <div class="onb4-head">
      <h1 class="onb4-h1">Eve ist erst der <span class="onb4-nb">Anfang<span class="onb4-dot"></span></span></h1>
      <p class="onb4-sub">Eve begleitet deine Gäste mitten im Aufenthalt — aber die Reise ist länger. Schon bald deckst du sie komplett ab: von der Direktbuchung bis zur Wiederkehr. Kein Muss, nur ein Ausblick.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="onb4-pillars">

      <!-- Vor der Anreise -->
      <article class="onb4-pillar">
        <span class="onb4-tag onb4-tag--soon">Bald</span>
        <span class="onb4-ico" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="onb4-phase">Vor der Anreise</span>
        <h2 class="onb4-ptitle">Direktbuchung</h2>
        <p class="onb4-pdesc">Gäste buchen direkt bei dir — ohne Portalprovision. Mehr Marge und die eigene Beziehung von der ersten Sekunde an.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Während (erledigt) -->
      <article class="onb4-pillar is-done">
        <span class="onb4-tag onb4-tag--done"><span class="onb4-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Erledigt</span>
        <span class="onb4-ico" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="onb4-phase">Während</span>
        <h2 class="onb4-ptitle">Gästemappe &amp; Eve</h2>
        <p class="onb4-pdesc">Dein digitaler Concierge ist live — rund um die Uhr, in 11 Sprachen. Genau das hast du gerade aufgesetzt.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Nach der Abreise -->
      <article class="onb4-pillar">
        <span class="onb4-tag onb4-tag--soon">Bald</span>
        <span class="onb4-ico" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="17 1 21 5 17 9"/><path d="M3 11V9a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h14"/>
            <polyline points="7 23 3 19 7 15"/><path d="M21 13v2a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="onb4-phase">Nach der Abreise</span>
        <h2 class="onb4-ptitle">Wallet, WhatsApp &amp; Wiederkehr</h2>
        <p class="onb4-pdesc">Bleib in Kontakt: Wallet-Karte aufs Handy, Nachrichten per WhatsApp, Anreize für den nächsten Besuch.</p>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="onb4-cta-row">
      <button type="button" class="onb4-next" data-onb-goto="5" title="Weitere Schritte folgen">Weiter →</button>
      <button type="button" class="onb4-skip" data-onb-action="skip">Setup überspringen</button>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Schritt-Balken — Schritt 4 aktiv, klickbar (vor/zurück) -->
  <div class="onb4-steps" role="group" aria-label="Onboarding-Schritte">
    {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(i => (
      <button
        type="button"
        class:list={['onb4-step', { 'is-active': i === 4 }]}
        data-onb-goto={i}
        aria-label={`Schritt ${i}`}
      ></button>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .onb4 {
    --petrol: #14616E;
    --petrol-soft: rgba(20, 97, 110, 0.06);
    max-width: 1140px; width: 100%;
    margin: 8px auto 12px;
    padding: 32px 32px 40px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    min-height: calc(100svh - var(--onb-chrome, 190px));
  }
  .onb4-body {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    gap: 36px;
  }

  /* Kopf (zentriert) */
  .onb4-head { text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .onb4-h1 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 5.2vw, 68px); line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em; color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 18px;
  }
  .onb4-nb { white-space: nowrap; }
  .onb4-dot {
    display: inline-block; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--petrol); margin-left: 4px; vertical-align: baseline;
  }
  .onb4-sub {
    font-family: 'Inter Tight', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-soft, rgba(10,10,10,0.65));
    margin: 0 auto; max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* Drei Säulen */
  .onb4-pillars {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 18px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 820px) { .onb4-pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto; } }

  .onb4-pillar {
    position: relative;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
    padding: 26px 22px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r, 12px);
    text-align: left;
  }
  .onb4-pillar.is-done {
    border-color: var(--petrol);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--petrol);
    background: var(--petrol-soft);
  }

  .onb4-tag {
    position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 8.5px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .onb4-tag--soon { color: var(--ink-faint, rgba(10,10,10,0.42)); border: 1px solid var(--border-medium, rgba(10,10,10,0.16)); }
  .onb4-tag--done { color: #fff; background: var(--petrol); }
  .onb4-check { font-size: 9px; line-height: 1; }

  .onb4-ico {
    width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 11px;
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    background: var(--bg-deep, #F0EFEA);
    color: var(--petrol); margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .onb4-pillar.is-done .onb4-ico { background: var(--petrol); color: #fff; }
  .onb4-ico svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }

  .onb4-phase {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted, rgba(10,10,10,0.45));
  }
  .onb4-pillar.is-done .onb4-phase { color: var(--petrol); }
  .onb4-ptitle {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--ink); margin: 0;
  }
  .onb4-pdesc {
    font-family: 'Inter Tight', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink-soft, rgba(10,10,10,0.6)); margin: 0;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .onb4-cta-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .onb4-next {
    appearance: none; -webkit-appearance: none; border: none;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--surface); background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--r, 12px); padding: 13px 26px;
    cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s ease;
  }
  .onb4-next:hover { background: var(--petrol); }
  .onb4-next:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: default; background: var(--ink); }
  .onb4-skip {
    appearance: none; -webkit-appearance: none; border: none;
    font-family: 'Inter Tight', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink-muted, rgba(10,10,10,0.42));
    background: transparent; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .onb4-skip:hover { color: var(--ink); }

  /* Schritt-Balken (segmentiert, klickbar — wie Screen 1–3) */
  .onb4-steps {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    margin: 28px auto 0;
  }
  .onb4-step {
    appearance: none; -webkit-appearance: none; padding: 0; border: none;
    flex: 0 0 auto; width: 20px; height: 5px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--border-medium, rgba(10,10,10,0.16));
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: width 0.3s ease, background 200ms ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
  }
  .onb4-step.is-active { width: 46px; background: var(--petrol); }
  .onb4-step:not(.is-active):not(:disabled):hover { background: var(--petrol); opacity: 0.45; }
  .onb4-step:disabled { cursor: default; }
</style>
